{"article_id":"4OSEfBZB5DvHMmBB","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"No question ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"Senate majority leader Mitch McConnell","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"( R )","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"of Kentucky blinked","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"when it came to funding the Department of Homeland Security .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"With the clock ticking toward a DHS shutdown Friday night","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"and Democrats repeatedly blocking debate on a funding bill","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"because it contained immigration \" poison pills , \"","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"the Senate leader gave Democrats what they wanted on Wednesday :","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"a \" clean \" funding bill , minus the toxic measure","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"to block President Obama ' s executive immigration action on immigration in November .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"That will be taken up separately .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Will House Speaker John Boehner","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"( R )","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"of Ohio also blink ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"and bring the clean bill","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"- expected to pass the Senate with a strong bipartisan vote -","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"to the floor ?","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Such a move would put him at odds with many in his caucus ,","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"and possibly prompt a challenge to his leadership .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"As weeks of struggle over DHS funding have shown ,","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Republican control of both chambers doesn ' t necessarily mean smooth sailing for the GOP .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"Even when the two leaders agree on policy","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"- as they do in this case -","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"they work under very different conditions ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"with each chamber having its own political climate and ways","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"of doing things .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Majority leader McConnell for instance , faces the unique challenge of the filibuster","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"- the Senate blocking device","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"that requires 60 votes","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"to overcome .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"With Republicans holding 54 seats ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"he needs at least six Democrats","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"to pass any controversial legislation , an incentive for at least a minimally bipartisan approach .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"He also has 24 senators up for reelection in 2016","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"- several of them from blue states .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"That encourages political flexibility .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Most GOP House seats , on the other hand , are secure in gerrymandered districts and red states .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"That promotes rigidity .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"\" McConnell has his own challenge .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"Having won a majority , and a bigger one","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"than he expected ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"he still has a challenge","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"in holding it .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"And holding it means showing","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"he can govern","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"and providing some protection for senators","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"who are up in Ohio , in Pennsylvania , in New Hampshire , \"","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"says Norman Ornstein , a resident scholar at the American Enterprise Institute in Washington .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"House Republicans , on the other hand , \" dominate \" in states such as Mississippi , Alabama , Oklahoma , Louisiana , and Texas ,","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Mr. Ornstein points out .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"\" These individual House districts are themselves homogeneous echo chambers . \"","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"You can hear the difference","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"when talking with Republicans from these two worlds .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"Republican Sen. Mark Kirk is up for reelection in Illinois ,","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"which Obama easily won in 2012 and 2008 .","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"He was an early supporter of a \" clean \" bill","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"to fully fund DHS","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"without the immigration riders .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"He wanted nothing to come between his state and the funding .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Senator Kirk recalls traveling through Chicago ' s O ' Hare Airport ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"which is a known potential terrorist target .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"\" Boy did I get an earful from the people","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"I represent , \"","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Senator Kirk says in a brief interview in the Senate basement , on the way to his office .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"\" Chicago doesn ' t work","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"unless US military protects the United States .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"We got ta have DHS . \"","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Kirk says","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"he ' s tried to be the consistent \" lone voice in the wilderness \" on DHS funding ,","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"and \" if our party doctrine was to mess the bill up ,","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"then to say","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"that the party doctrine was wrong ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"and we should just pass clean DHS . \"","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"But just a five-minute walk away , on the House side of the Capitol , Rep. John Fleming","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"( R )","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"of Louisiana holds the opposite view .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"A tea party favorite , he faced no Democratic opponent in his reelection bid of 2010 ,","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"but he did face a Libertarian one .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"In a scrum of reporters , Congressman Fleming said","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"a potential DHS shutdown did not come up at a closed GOP House conference Wednesday morning .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"The real question ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"he continued ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"is the president ' s November executive action","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"that would shield millions of undocumented immigrants from deportation .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"That ' s executive overreach and unconstitutional ,","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"he and other Republicans say .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"In January , the House GOP passed a DHS funding bill","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"that also blocked funding for that program .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"\" The only tool","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"we have in Congress","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"to block an unconstitutional act","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"that would severely damage Americans for generations to come","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"is to deplete the funding of that very executive action ,","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"and that ' s what our bill does","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"and that ' s what we intend to do , \"","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"When asked what his constituents think should be done about the funding issue ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"\" We don ' t get a lot of calls","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"because they know my position on this .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"If I deviated ,","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"they ' d be very upset . \"","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"Indeed , conservatives such as Fleming would be very angry","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"if Boehner decided to bring a clean DHS bill to the House floor .","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"Many have said","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"they would not vote for a bill","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"that did not also block the president ' s immigration action ,","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"and they ' re supported by conservative bloggers and outside groups","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"who are already screaming about a cave-in .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"Some House Republicans might even try to stage a leadership coup .","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"In January , 25 Republicans voted for someone other than Boehner for speaker .","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"While McConnell faces his challenge of 60 votes ,","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"the speaker ' s challenge is to keep his diverse caucus in line","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"so he can reach the magic target of 218 , the number of votes","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"needed","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"to pass a bill in the House .","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"Republicans hold 247 seats ,","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"but with a diverse caucus , it ' s a challenge getting to 218 .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"Boehner likens it to keeping frogs in a wheelbarrow ,","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"and on controversial legislation","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"- such as the budget -","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"he ' s had to turn to Democrats for votes . \"","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"For Boehner ,","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"just as it has been for the last few years ,","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"his challenge is how many times can he bring up things for passage","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"that will require more Democrats ,","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"and","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"when he brings those up ,","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"can he be sure","depth":15},{"id":130,"text":"he ' ll get enough Republicans","depth":16},{"id":131,"text":"to add to the Democrats ? \"","depth":16},{"id":132,"text":"Ornstein says .","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"If DHS is to be fully funded ,","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"a bill","depth":15},{"id":135,"text":"that kills the president ' s executive action","depth":15},{"id":136,"text":"won ' t be part of it","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"-","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"that much has been made clear by the Senate showdown .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"Boehner will either have to bring his caucus around ,","depth":7},{"id":140,"text":"or turn to House Democrats","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"to buttress his numbers ,","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"with a fallback position being a stopgap continuing resolution .","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":144,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":145,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":146,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":147,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":148,"text":"\" I think","depth":5},{"id":149,"text":"Boehner in his gut knows","depth":6},{"id":150,"text":"that he ' s going to have to face reality here , \"","depth":6},{"id":151,"text":"says a Republican House member ,","depth":5},{"id":152,"text":"speaking on background .","depth":5},{"id":153,"text":"\" It ' s just a matter of the speaker being able to articulate this to those members","depth":4},{"id":154,"text":"- to the ' hell no ' caucus ,","depth":5},{"id":155,"text":"who are going to be unhappy with anything short of a complete and total victory . \"","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":311,"left":298,"right":310,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":209,"right":297,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":209,"left":175,"right":208,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":167,"right":174,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":167,"left":160,"right":166,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":0,"right":159,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":159,"left":158,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":157,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":157,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":165,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearit